---
import { Briefcase, ArrowRight } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section id="experience" class="mb-40 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24">
  <div
    class="mb-16 flex items-end justify-between border-b border-slate-200 pb-8 transition-colors dark:border-surface-container-low"
  >
    <div>
      <h2 class="font-headline mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">Professional Arc</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-slate-600 dark:text-on-surface-variant">Experience and impact.</p>
    </div>
    <Briefcase class="h-10 w-10 shrink-0 text-blue-600 opacity-50 dark:text-primary md:h-11 md:w-11" stroke-width={1.25} aria-hidden="true" />
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-12 border-l border-slate-200 pl-4 transition-colors dark:border-outline-variant/30 md:pl-8">
    <div class="group relative">
      <div
        class="absolute -left-[33px] top-1 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-2 border-blue-600 bg-slate-50 transition-colors group-hover:bg-blue-600 dark:-left-[41px] md:-left-[49px] dark:border-primary dark:bg-surface dark:group-hover:bg-primary"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="ml-6 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:border-transparent dark:bg-surface-container-low dark:shadow-none dark:hover:bg-surface-container"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline mb-1 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Software Development Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium text-blue-600 dark:text-primary">Lumen Technologies</p>
            <p class="mt-1 font-body text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-on-surface-variant">Bangalore, India · July 2023 – Present</p>
          </div>
          <span class="font-label mt-2 block text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 dark:text-on-surface-variant md:mt-0"
            >Current</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 font-body leading-relaxed text-slate-600 dark:text-on-surface-variant">
          <p class="flex gap-3">
            <ArrowRight class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-blue-600 dark:text-primary" stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" />
            <span
              >Modernized legacy enterprise services—including Address Matcher—from Restlet to <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">Spring Boot</strong>, improving maintainability and performance.</span
            >
          </p>
          <p class="flex gap-3">
            <ArrowRight class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-blue-600 dark:text-primary" stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" />
            <span
              >Delivered <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">GCP</strong>-hosted, containerized workloads on <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">Kubernetes</strong> via <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">Rancher</strong>.</span
            >
          </p>
          <p class="flex gap-3">
            <ArrowRight class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-blue-600 dark:text-primary" stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" />
            <span
              >Owned the <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">GEOAM Address Matching API</strong>—external REST for AJAX address completion—with reliability improvements for Blue Marble, GEOES, and RPA consumers.</span
            >
          </p>
          <p class="flex gap-3">
            <ArrowRight class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-blue-600 dark:text-primary" stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" />
            <span
              >Enhanced <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">LOOPQUAL</strong> and <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">LOOPQUAL-BATCH</strong> with <strong class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-on-surface">RabbitMQ</strong>-driven ingestion from upstream systems.</span
            >
          </p>
          <p class="flex gap-3">
            <ArrowRight class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-blue-600 dark:text-primary" stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" />
            <span
              >Deepened observability with Splunk, AppDynamics, and Datadog; supported incidents across cloud and legacy estates.</span
            >
          </p>
          <p class="flex gap-3">
            <ArrowRight class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-blue-600 dark:text-primary" stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" />
            <span
              >Maintained the ASP.NET Maintenance Recommendation Application (Azure AD SSO) with incremental fixes and stability work.</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
